news.title: Navi Mumbai: SC orders 165 families out to raze illegal buildings
news.para: The apex court has ordered the 165 families residing in these "towers of corruption", as Krishna Complex and Trimurti Park are called by activists, to give a written undertaking that they will shift out within six months.

news.title: Gururgram: Illegal farmhouse, three multi-storey buildings razed
news.para: District town planner (enforcement) Amit Madholia said that the colony is a zero tolerance area for any construction activity but some miscreants are carrying out illegal constructions.

news.title: Jaypee offers to finish incomplete Sports City projects in next two years
news.para: JAL had approached the court against YEIDA’s order cancelling the allotment of 1,085 hectares of land given to the developer about three years ago. The next date of hearing is December 12.
